National Assembly and National Council of Provinces: President’s reply to the debate on the State-of-the-nation Address Cape Town City Hall, Hybrid Meeting Platform, 16th February 2022, 14:00 – 15:30 * Editor's note: This livestream has ended. You may watch a recording above. CAPE TOWN - President Cyril  Ramaphosa is responding to questions about his State of the Nation Address. It's been a heated few days in City Hall. Opposition parties have asked Ramaphosa a number of questions including how he plans on implementing what he said at SONA.